# Site Tasks Chrome Plugin

Current Version: none ( under development ) 

Site Tasks Chrome Plugin allows you to interact with WordPress Site Tasks plugin to create tasks on per page bases.

## Features

### Version 1.0
* Ability to create tasks
* Ability to add attachements to tasks
* Ability to comment on tasks
* Allows to login to WP if user not logged in

### Version 1.1
* Ability to capture screenshots using [Google Chrome Screen Capture Plugin](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/cpngackimfmofbokmjmljamhdncknpmg) and attaching them to the page
